OL,3,CBlue Islands collapse to trigger 100
OL,4,Cjob losses
OL,6,FAround 100 Blue Islands staff are set
OL,7,Fto potentially lose their jobs
OL,8,Ffollowing the company's suspension of
OL,9,Fall trading.
OL,11,FThe regional airline, which has its
OL,12,Foperational headquarters based in
OL,13,FGuernsey, announced on Friday night
OL,14,Fthat it had ceased trading and
OL,15,Fcancelled all future flights.
OL,17,FThe company had been locked in talks
OL,18,Fwith Jersey's government before the
OL,19,Fannouncement, ITV News understands.
