OL,6,FHe said: "I hope the workers will be
OL,7,Fable to find a place with other
OL,8,Forganisations as soon as possible.
OL,10,F"Their skills are certainly highly
OL,11,Fsought after at the moment.
OL,13,F"Hopefully they'll be absorbed by
OL,14,Fother airlines looking to take the
OL,15,Fstrain in Blue Islands' absence."
