OL,6,FAurigny initially announced that it
OL,7,Fwould place a temporary schedule of
OL,8,Fflights between Guernsey and
OL,9,FSouthampton, as well as between
OL,10,FGuernsey and Jersey, until Wednesday,
OL,11,F19 November, following Blue Islands'
OL,12,Fcollapse.
OL,14,FOn Saturday evening, this was extended
OL,15,Funtil 17 December, with flights
OL,16,Frunning as often as three times a day
OL,17,Fbetween Guernsey and Southampton, and
OL,18,Fup to twice daily between the
OL,19,FBailiwick and Jersey.
