OL,6,FNico Bezuidenhout, Aurigny's CEO, said
OL,7,Fsome of the jobs lost could be taken
OL,8,Fon by Aurigny, adding: "We've always
OL,9,Frespected Blue Islands and their staff.
OL,11,F"They've got good staff and they ran a
OL,12,Fgood business.
OL,14,F"To the extent that opportunities do
OL,15,Fexist, we will almost certainly
OL,16,Fwelcome and be in contact with a
OL,17,Fnumber of staff."
